Nice roscoe. Porter.

1074
01:09:56.313 --> 01:09:57.839
Heavy enough
to be a nutcracker.

1075
01:09:57.913 --> 01:09:59.919
We'll be in touch.
Rocky.

1076
01:10:01.655 --> 01:10:03.660
Keep up
the good work!

1077
01:10:05.588 --> 01:10:08.237
Nobody likes
a monkey on their back.

1078
01:10:08.306 --> 01:10:09.832
I had 3...

1079
01:10:09.905 --> 01:10:12.718
and they were cramping
my style.

1080
01:10:12.783 --> 01:10:15.563
I was gonna have
to lighten the load.

1081
01:10:49.954 --> 01:10:51.610
Porter.

1082
01:10:51.681 --> 01:10:53.207
Where have you been?

1083
01:10:53.279 --> 01:10:55.285
