1093
01:11:26.540 --> 01:11:28.327
So why did you?

1094
01:11:30.058 --> 01:11:31.431
Yeah. you're right.

1095
01:11:34.055 --> 01:11:36.388
When I came back...

1096
01:11:36.453 --> 01:11:38.624
I came back here
with nothing.

1097
01:11:40.131 --> 01:11:42.137
No life.

1098
01:11:42.209 --> 01:11:43.256
No hope.

1099
01:11:44.608 --> 01:11:46.462
You were the only
good thing in my life...

1100
01:11:46.528 --> 01:11:48.218
that hadn't been
taken from me.

1101
01:11:51.293 --> 01:11:53.332
I couldn't stay away.

1102
01:11:54.363 --> 01:11:55.737
I had to see you...

1103
01:11:55.802 --> 01:11:57.709
just to make sure
I wasn't in hell.

1104
01:12:01.079 --> 01:12:03.216
So why don't
we get out of here?

1105
01:12:03.286 --> 01:12:04.528
We can't.

1106
01:12:04.596 --> 01:12:05.806
Why?

1107
01:12:05.876 --> 01:12:07.085
Well. you said it.

1108
01:12:07.154 --> 01:12:08.975
They're not gonna stop
until they bury us.

1109
01:12:11.791 --> 01:12:12.773
So...

1110
01:12:12.847 --> 01:12:15.748
So we bury them first.

1111
01:12:59.378 --> 01:13:01.320
I should've quit.

1112
01:13:08.174 --> 01:13:10.562
I should've driven you
somewhere else.

1113
01:13:53.042 --> 01:13:53.934
Hey. look.

1114
01:13:54.001 --> 01:13:56.683
Hey. look.

1115
01:13:58.480 --> 01:13:59.372
Whoa.

1116
01:13:59.439 --> 01:14:01.031
That's me!
That's me!

1117
01:14:15.684 --> 01:14:17.690
Happy birthday. Johnny.

1118
01:14:20.257 --> 01:14:21.630
What's next?

1119
01:14:21.696 --> 01:14:23.289
You're the man.

1120
01:14:23.359 --> 01:14:25.214
You're totally the man.
This is your night.

1121
01:14:25.279 --> 01:14:26.652
Hey. Johnny.

1122
01:14:33.433 --> 01:14:35.603
I'm your birthday present.

1123
01:14:35.672 --> 01:14:37.678
Who is that?

1124
01:14:37.751 --> 01:14:39.441
