Yes!

1125
01:14:39.510 --> 01:14:40.403
We didn't do it.

1126
01:14:40.469 --> 01:14:41.581
We had nothing
to do with this.

1127
01:14:41.653 --> 01:14:43.756
Dude.
she's so hot.

1128
01:14:43.827 --> 01:14:44.775
Get her.

1129
01:14:44.850 --> 01:14:45.744
She's so fine.

1130
01:14:45.810 --> 01:14:46.921
Go! Go!

1131
01:14:46.993 --> 01:14:48.203
Can you believe
this guy?

1132
01:14:48.273 --> 01:14:49.995
Second Friend: Dad's really
hooking him up. isn't he?

1133
01:14:50.063 --> 01:14:52.550
Boy. you are cute.
aren't you?

1134
01:14:53.900 --> 01:14:57.673
