'cause I'm not cheap.

1136
01:15:05.031 --> 01:15:06.720
Don't wait up. boys.

1137
01:15:07.908 --> 01:15:10.241
I promise he won't be home
before midnight.

1138
01:15:13.793 --> 01:15:14.686
See you. man!

1139
01:15:16.544 --> 01:15:18.332
Damn!

1140
01:15:29.624 --> 01:15:31.990
Mmm. That's a good boy.

1141
01:15:32.054 --> 01:15:33.578
OK.

1142
01:15:33.652 --> 01:15:35.178
Yeah. right there.

1143
01:15:46.444 --> 01:15:48.450
Relax.

1144
01:15:48.523 --> 01:15:50.856
Who's the professional
here. Johnny?

1145
01:15:51.882 --> 01:15:53.888
So go with it.

1146
01:15:53.961 --> 01:15:55.967
I promise
you won't regret it.

1147
01:15:57.063 --> 01:15:59.645
There. baby.

1148
01:16:08.927 --> 01:16:10.617
Hello.

1149
01:16:14.043 --> 01:16:15.090
Relax. kid.

1150
01:16:15.164 --> 01:16:16.505
