1151
01:16:19.513 --> 01:16:21.007
Get hurt?

1152
01:16:21.080 --> 01:16:23.087
What's he talking about?

1153
01:16:23.158 --> 01:16:24.269
Shh.

1154
01:16:26.260 --> 01:16:27.616
The thrill is gone

1155
01:16:29.823 --> 01:16:32.789
The thrill is gone away

1156
01:16:36.219 --> 01:16:38.072
The thrill is gone.
baby...

1157
01:16:38.138 --> 01:16:39.828
Good to have you
back in town...

1158
01:16:39.896 --> 01:16:40.943
Mr.Fairfax.

1159
01:16:41.016 --> 01:16:42.706
