with you?

1164
01:16:50.610 --> 01:16:51.820
Sorry.
Mr.Fairfax.

1165
01:16:52.849 --> 01:16:53.896
Hello.
Mr.Fairfax.

1166
01:16:53.967 --> 01:16:55.341
How's it going.
Charlie?

1167
01:16:57.486 --> 01:16:58.860
