a short conversation.

1169
01:17:05.929 --> 01:17:07.586
Well. between us and
our neighborhood cops...

1170
01:17:07.655 --> 01:17:09.989
I'd say we got him
pretty well covered. huh?

1171
01:17:12.612 --> 01:17:14.783
Walter. wake up.

1172
01:17:16.131 --> 01:17:17.656
Walter!

1173
01:17:17.729 --> 01:17:19.070
Wake up!

1174
01:17:19.136 --> 01:17:22.102
Keep those bags up.
boys.

1175
01:17:22.175 --> 01:17:23.418
Come on.

1176
01:17:23.486 --> 01:17:26.234
