1177
01:17:26.300 --> 01:17:27.893
I'm the reason
you're home early...

1178
01:17:27.962 --> 01:17:29.042
Mr.Fairfax.

1179
01:17:30.681 --> 01:17:31.760
You're Porter?

1180
01:17:31.833 --> 01:17:33.971
That's it. Keep them up.
boys. at shoulder level.

1181
01:17:34.040 --> 01:17:35.348
Drop them.
and I'll drill you.

1182
01:17:39.797 --> 01:17:41.649
Well. what'll
