1190
01:17:56.521 --> 01:17:57.415
But that poor
buck-toothed bastard's...

1191
01:17:57.481 --> 01:17:59.335
probably better off dead
anyway.

1192
01:18:00.999 --> 01:18:02.689
He'd probably
let me die. too.

1193
01:18:02.758 --> 01:18:05.571
