he thought I was bluffing.

1194
01:18:05.636 --> 01:18:07.009
Try him.

1195
01:18:07.075 --> 01:18:09.529
You might find him more
receptive than you think.

1196
01:18:11.393 --> 01:18:12.341
All right.

1197
01:18:13.823 --> 01:18:15.448
