1198
01:18:18.108 --> 01:18:19.797
Hello.

1199
01:18:19.867 --> 01:18:21.872
Well. it's like this...

1200
01:18:21.946 --> 01:18:23.669
I'm standing
in my living room...

1201
01:18:23.737 --> 01:18:25.329
and there's a man here
named Porter...

1202
01:18:25.401 --> 01:18:26.676
who says that
he expects you...

1203
01:18:26.744 --> 01:18:28.400
to pay him sooner
or later.

1204
01:18:29.462 --> 01:18:31.948
Yes. of course.

1205
01:18:32.021 --> 01:18:33.677
He wants to talk to you.

1206
01:18:33.746 --> 01:18:35.817
Put it
on the speaker.

1207
01:18:40.335 --> 01:18:41.708
This is Porter.

1208
01:18:41.773 --> 01:18:43.463
Bronson:
You got balls. Porter.

1209
01:18:43.534 --> 01:18:45.865
You're proving to be
a real pain in the ass...

1210
01:18:45.931 --> 01:18:47.010
a mosquito.

1211
01:18:47.082 --> 01:18:50.376
To get rid of you.
I'll swat you with 130 grand.

1212
01:18:50.441 --> 01:18:51.618
Ah.

1213
01:18:51.687 --> 01:18:53.345
It's not 130--

1214
01:18:55.046 --> 01:18:57.315
Hey. what the hell
are you doing. man?

1215
01:18:57.381 --> 01:18:58.753
Fairfax? Fairfax.

1216
01:18:58.819 --> 01:19:00.193
Yes. Oh. it's all right.

1217
01:19:00.258 --> 01:19:01.948
He's just killing
my alligator bags...

1218
01:19:02.018 --> 01:19:03.872
and shooting holes
in my suits.

1219
01:19:03.937 --> 01:19:06.903
That's just mean.
That's mean. man.

1220
01:19:06.974 --> 01:19:07.868
You people
aren't listening.

1221
01:19:07.934 --> 01:19:09.427
It's not 130 gr--

1222
01:19:09.501 --> 01:19:10.394
No. you listen.

1223
01:19:10.460 --> 01:19:11.703
I'll get you your money...

1224
01:19:11.771 --> 01:19:13.624
but you're never gonna
live to enjoy it.

1225
01:19:13.690 --> 01:19:16.023
You let me
worry about that.

1226
01:19:16.089 --> 01:19:17.136
Here's the deal.

1227
01:19:17.209 --> 01:19:18.931
I want you to deliver
the money yourself.

1228
01:19:20.087 --> 01:19:21.777
You're one hell
of an optimist.

1229
01:19:21.846 --> 01:19:23.438
What in the world
makes you think...

1230
01:19:23.509 --> 01:19:25.165
I'm gonna deliver
the money myself?

1231
01:19:25.235 --> 01:19:26.445
Well. if you don't...

1232
01:19:26.514 --> 01:19:28.106
you'll never see
little Johnny again.

1233
01:19:29.681 --> 01:19:31.403
Didn't come home from
the fight last night...

1234
01:19:31.471 --> 01:19:32.485
did he?

1235
01:19:32.560 --> 01:19:34.085
He's a good-looking kid...

1236
01:19:34.158 --> 01:19:35.684
but you indulge him
too much.

1237
01:19:35.757 --> 01:19:37.130
I told him so.

1238
01:19:37.196 --> 01:19:38.406
Bullshit.

1239
01:19:38.475 --> 01:19:39.936
You haven't got him.

1240
01:19:40.010 --> 01:19:41.864
You wouldn't be
that stupid.

1241
01:19:41.929 --> 01:19:43.903
My dad never bought me
a Ferrari.

1242
01:19:43.976 --> 01:19:46.245
I had to steal
my first one.

1243
01:19:46.311 --> 01:19:48.644
Nice inscription
on the key chain.

1244
01:19:48.710 --> 01:19:50.911
A little sappy.
Want me to read it?

1245
01:19:50.979 --> 01:19:52.888
You're dead. Porter.

1246
01:19:52.962 --> 01:19:54.969
Nobody fucks
with my family.

1247
01:19:55.040 --> 01:19:56.186
You hear me?

1248
01:19:57.280 --> 01:19:58.654
You're a dead man.

1249
01:19:58.720 --> 01:20:00.573
That's Johnny.
Mr.Bronson...

1250
01:20:00.639 --> 01:20:02.328
unless you turn up
with the money.

1251
01:20:03.835 --> 01:20:05.361
Is that a yes?

1252
01:20:05.435 --> 01:20:06.579
Hmm?

1253
01:20:06.650 --> 01:20:08.405
What's the matter.
cat got your crotch?

1254
01:20:09.913 --> 01:20:12.561
Some decisions are hard.
Mr.Bronson.

1255
01:20:12.631 --> 01:20:13.710
Where?

1256
01:20:14.742 --> 01:20:16.016
I'll let you know.

1257
01:20:16.085 --> 01:20:17.676
I'll be in touch.

1258
01:20:23.984 --> 01:20:25.837
You just signed
your own death warrant...

1259
01:20:25.902 --> 01:20:27.243
for $130.000.

1260
01:20:27.309 --> 01:20:28.552
I don't--
I don't get that.

1261
01:20:28.620 --> 01:20:30.244
What is it?

1262
01:20:30.315 --> 01:20:31.842
The principle
or something. huh?

1263
01:20:33.098 --> 01:20:34.952
Stop it.
I'm getting misty.

1264
01:20:35.017 --> 01:20:36.870
And tell him it's 70.
will you?

1265
01:20:38.023 --> 01:20:40.357
70?

1266
01:20:40.422 --> 01:20:41.828
What do you mean
it's only 70?

1267
01:20:41.893 --> 01:20:43.582
Only 70.000?

1268
01:20:43.651 --> 01:20:46.301
Hell. my suits are worth
more than that!

1269
01:20:48.129 --> 01:20:49.721
Aw. man.

1270
01:20:49.792 --> 01:20:51.417
Listen to this:

1271
01:20:51.487 --> 01:20:53.820
"Ocean Ray Sundancer.

1272
01:20:53.885 --> 01:20:55.258
Icemaker.

1273
01:20:55.324 --> 01:20:57.657
Camper canvas.

1274
01:20:57.722 --> 01:20:59.577
Vacuum flush head."

1275
01:21:00.601 --> 01:21:02.291
80.000 bucks.

1276
01:21:03.639 --> 01:21:05.810
I'm telling you.
you ain't gonna have it.

1277
01:21:05.879 --> 01:21:07.088
You wanna bet?

1278
01:21:07.157 --> 01:21:09.010
No. I don't wanna bet.

1279
01:21:09.075 --> 01:21:11.081
I'm out 150 already.

1280
01:21:12.434 --> 01:21:14.440
150 I'm getting
my damn boat.

1281
01:21:14.513 --> 01:21:16.367
Better come down
with something.

1282
01:21:16.432 --> 01:21:17.544
Hey. hey.

1283
01:21:17.615 --> 01:21:20.198
Hicks. Leary.

1284
01:21:20.269 --> 01:21:22.122
We're Holland
and Vanowen.

1285
01:21:22.188 --> 01:21:24.227
Internal Affairs.

1286
01:21:26.666 --> 01:21:28.933
You boys wanna back off?
We're on a stakeout here.

1287
01:21:30.023 --> 01:21:31.680
Wanna step out
of the car. please?

1288
01:21:31.751 --> 01:21:33.156
What for?

1289
01:21:33.221 --> 01:21:35.423
I think you better
step out of the car detectives.

1290
01:21:47.708 --> 01:21:50.009
What the hell's
going on?

1291
01:21:50.074 --> 01:21:51.634
I don't know.

1292
01:21:51.706 --> 01:21:53.592
Is this your badge.
Detective?

1293
01:21:53.656 --> 01:21:56.372
The one
you reported missing?

1294
01:21:58.101 --> 01:21:59.442
Yeah.
Where'd you find it?

1295
01:21:59.510 --> 01:22:01.166
Where exactly
did you lose it?

1296
01:22:05.458 --> 01:22:07.886
Does this belong
to you?

1297
01:22:12.478 --> 01:22:14.234
It's Porter.
Follow him.

1298
01:22:14.302 --> 01:22:16.341
I got that motherfucker.

1299
01:22:28.789 --> 01:22:29.999
Hey.

1300
01:22:36.432 --> 01:22:38.153
Get in. Porter.

1301
01:22:44.555 --> 01:22:45.732
Close the door.

1302
01:22:49.864 --> 01:22:52.001
Now set the roscoe
on the floor.

1303
01:22:54.212 --> 01:22:55.106
Slow!

1304
01:22:59.299 --> 01:23:03.322
See. I'm gonna turn you in
to the outfit for a reward.

1305
01:23:03.390 --> 01:23:05.113
And maybe
they'll be so impressed...

1306
01:23:05.182 --> 01:23:06.425
that they'll ask me
to join...

1307
01:23:06.493 --> 01:23:08.467
and I'll be on easy street.

1308
01:23:08.541 --> 01:23:10.547
Medical. dental.

1309
01:23:11.578 --> 01:23:13.813
I'm just-- I'm gonna
walk you right in.

1310
01:23:13.882 --> 01:23:16.727
Porter on the hoof.

1311
01:23:16.791 --> 01:23:19.026
Unless you get
rambunctious.

1312
01:23:19.094 --> 01:23:21.232
Then I'll just have to
take care of you mysel--

1313
01:23:24.851 --> 01:23:26.824
You're not gonna
fuckin' kill me. are you?

1314
01:23:36.908 --> 01:23:38.815
Now.

1315
01:23:44.326 --> 01:23:46.114
Hubba hubba hubba.

1316
01:24:07.097 --> 01:24:08.110
Aah!

1317
01:25:12.272 --> 01:25:14.660
Hey! Who are you?
What are you doing?

1318
01:25:14.734 --> 01:25:15.748
Hey. fatboy!

1319
01:25:16.782 --> 01:25:18.636
Yeah.
I'm talking to you.

1320
01:25:24.648 --> 01:25:25.663
Fat.

1321
01:25:42.335 --> 01:25:43.283
Mmm.

1322
01:25:43.358 --> 01:25:44.851
Ohh.

1323
01:25:46.236 --> 01:25:48.145
Aw. stop it. stop it.

1324
01:25:49.211 --> 01:25:50.932
I hate this. I hate it.

1325
01:25:54.806 --> 01:25:56.333
Look at this
stinking place.

1326
01:25:56.406 --> 01:25:59.055
My-- Porter.
what's the matter with you?

1327
01:25:59.124 --> 01:26:00.552
Just tell us where he is...

1328
01:26:00.628 --> 01:26:02.515
so we can get the hell
out of here. huh?

1329
01:26:02.579 --> 01:26:03.854
Come on.

1330
01:26:13.036 --> 01:26:14.344
Too late now.

1331
01:26:17.832 --> 01:26:20.646
He doesn't wanna
say anything.

1332
01:26:20.711 --> 01:26:22.085
He just wants to
get himself beat up...

1333
01:26:22.150 --> 01:26:23.971
that's all.

1334
01:26:28.387 --> 01:26:30.240
Here it is.

1335
01:26:30.305 --> 01:26:31.864
130.000.

1336
01:26:34.846 --> 01:26:36.220
That's as close...

1337
01:26:36.285 --> 01:26:38.040
as you're ever
gonna get to it...

1338
01:26:38.109 --> 01:26:39.929
but I'll make you
a deal.

1339
01:26:39.995 --> 01:26:41.684
Tell me where John is...

1340
01:26:41.753 --> 01:26:43.608
and I'll finish you quick.

1341
01:26:43.673 --> 01:26:45.526
I promise
you won't have to find out...

1342
01:26:45.591 --> 01:26:47.216
what your left ball
tastes like.

1343
01:26:50.549 --> 01:26:53.199
But if there's even
a bruise on him...

1344
01:26:53.267 --> 01:26:55.370
I'll make this last
3 weeks.

1345
01:26:55.441 --> 01:26:57.512
I'll give you
a blood transfusion...

1346
01:26:57.584 --> 01:26:59.820
to keep you alive
if I have to.

1347
01:27:02.893 --> 01:27:04.899
Where is he?

1348
01:27:35.033 --> 01:27:36.854
I'm waiting.

1349
01:27:41.494 --> 01:27:43.565
This little piggy
went to the market.

1350
01:27:48.657 --> 01:27:49.704
Aah! Shit!

1351
01:27:56.941 --> 01:27:58.499
I'm listening.

1352
01:28:08.614 --> 01:28:10.848
This little piggy
stayed home.

1353
01:28:15.264 --> 01:28:18.045
It's starting to look
like roast beef.

1354
01:28:20.957 --> 01:28:22.843
8 to go.

1355
01:28:22.908 --> 01:28:25.111
Then it's your knees.
Porter.

1356
01:28:25.178 --> 01:28:27.828
You can guess
where we go from there.

1357
01:28:27.897 --> 01:28:29.554
Where is he?

1358
01:28:36.149 --> 01:28:37.674
OK.

1359
01:28:37.747 --> 01:28:38.891
Hmm?

1360
01:28:39.962 --> 01:28:41.270
OK.

1361
01:28:42.297 --> 01:28:43.758
24...

1362
01:28:44.823 --> 01:28:46.678
24 Fielding.

1363
01:28:47.829 --> 01:28:49.258
Apartment 11.

1364
01:28:52.179 --> 01:28:53.520
You'll understand...

1365
01:28:53.586 --> 01:28:55.373
if I don't
entirely trust you.

1366
01:28:57.680 --> 01:28:59.140
Put him
in the trunk.

1367
01:28:59.215 --> 01:29:00.644
We'll take him along.

1368
01:29:01.678 --> 01:29:03.759
Let's go.
tough guy.

1369
01:29:29.951 --> 01:29:31.641
You two.
watch the front.

1370
01:29:35.452 --> 01:29:37.012
Aah!

1371
01:29:43.383 --> 01:29:44.593
Fuck.

1372
01:29:44.662 --> 01:29:46.035
Come on. Porter.

1373
01:29:52.274 --> 01:29:53.222
Hey. do me a favor.

1374
01:29:53.297 --> 01:29:55.052
Give me your lighter
for a second.

1375
01:30:56.139 --> 01:30:57.763
Come on.

1376
01:31:12.033 --> 01:31:13.974
What the hell's going on?

1377
01:31:14.047 --> 01:31:16.217
You were right
not to trust me.

1378
01:31:40.688 --> 01:31:42.475
Help... me.

1379
01:31:44.845 --> 01:31:46.404
Get out.

1380
01:32:25.962 --> 01:32:27.335
Come on. Porter.

1381
01:32:27.401 --> 01:32:29.124
It's been fun.
See you later. kid.

1382
01:32:29.192 --> 01:32:30.401
Hey! Come back here!

1383
01:32:30.471 --> 01:32:32.128
You bitch!

1384
01:32:32.198 --> 01:32:34.302
Come on. Porter.
Let's go.

1385
01:32:34.372 --> 01:32:35.834
What took you
so long?

1386
01:32:35.908 --> 01:32:37.184
Oh. hi. Rosie.

1387
01:32:37.251 --> 01:32:38.233
Come on.

1388
01:32:38.307 --> 01:32:39.680
Come on.
Porter.

1389
01:32:39.745 --> 01:32:40.639
Ahh.

1390
01:32:40.705 --> 01:32:41.882
Come on.

1391
01:32:41.953 --> 01:32:43.893
Get in there.

1392
01:32:43.966 --> 01:32:45.428
Good boy.

1393
01:32:46.941 --> 01:32:47.988
Good.

1394
01:32:49.339 --> 01:32:51.672
Oh. my God.
What happened to you?

1395
01:32:51.738 --> 01:32:53.014
I got hammered.

1396
01:32:53.081 --> 01:32:54.739
Are you OK?

1397
01:32:56.055 --> 01:32:57.429
Yeah.

1398
01:33:05.170 --> 01:33:06.446
You got it.

1399
01:33:06.513 --> 01:33:08.649
Piece of cake.

1400
01:33:12.814 --> 01:33:13.926
Where to?

1401
01:33:16.044 --> 01:33:18.464
Just drive. baby.

1402
01:33:22.374 --> 01:33:24.229
We were going
for breakfast...

1403
01:33:25.253 --> 01:33:26.779
in Canada.

1404
01:33:28.131 --> 01:33:29.986
We made a deal.

1405
01:33:30.051 --> 01:33:32.384
If she'd stop hooking...

1406
01:33:32.450 --> 01:33:34.302
I'd stop shooting people.

1407
01:33:36.606 --> 01:33:38.776
Maybe we were aiming high.

1408
01:33:39.305 --> 01:34:39.386
